ut I know this is the wrong way :</p>  <pre><code> $validator     -&gt;add('end_nb_min', 'notEmpty', [                         'rule' =&gt; ['comparison', '&lt;' ,'start_nb_min'],                         'message' =&gt; __('End time must be above start time')                 ]); </code></pre>  <p>Any suggestion would be appreciated.</p>